{"view":"article","slug":"pyraminx-cycle-lbl","category":"Pyraminx","subcategory":null,"topDir":"Pyraminx","title":{"en":"金字塔循环层先法"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>金字塔循环层先法</strong></p><p>还原尖</p><p>转体将非黄尖放到顶层；左右转体让一楼黄心朝前，在左侧就左手下， 在右侧就右手下；重复该步骤，将所有3个黄心都放到底面形成黄飞镖</p><p>左右转体让二楼黄棱朝前，转底层让心的颜色是黄棱的侧面格的颜色。黄棱在左就左手下下上上，黄棱在右就右手下下上上；重复该步骤，将所有3个黄棱都放到底面形成黄底层</p><p>左右转体和转底层让前面是蓝飞镖，倒下来转体让它到底面，用之前的方法还原蓝底层</p><p>左右转体和转底层让前面是黄飞镖，倒下来转体让它到底面，用之前的方法还原黄底层</p><p>左右转体和转底层让前面是蓝飞镖，倒下来转体让它到底面，用之前的方法还原蓝底层</p><p><strong>转动记号</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>上</strong></p><p><strong>R</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>下</strong></p><p><strong>R'</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>左</strong></p><p><strong>U</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>B</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>下下上上</strong></p></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr><tr><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td><td></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>S = R' L R L', H = L R' L' R.</p><p><strong>结构</strong></p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>心 [4]</p></td><td><p>棱 [6]</p></td><td><p>尖 [4]</p></td><td><p>角 [4]</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p>可在任何阶段还原尖.</p><p><strong>底心</strong></p><p>将非黄尖放在顶层，然后将三个黄心转到底面.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R'</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>L'</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>B</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>B'</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div>"},"algs":[],"thumb":"/stats/data/alg/media/pyraminx-cycle-lbl/en/image2.svg","warningCount":0,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
